441
00:41:49,080 --> 00:41:50,500
Doktore!

442
00:41:50,500 --> 00:41:53,870
Prosím! Buďte moudrý.

443
00:41:55,750 --> 00:41:57,420
Luno.

444
00:41:59,240 --> 00:42:01,360
To jsou hluboká slova.

445
00:42:04,530 --> 00:42:06,270
Ale moje volba...

446
00:42:07,740 --> 00:42:09,950
je tohle.

447
00:42:19,460 --> 00:42:22,980
Bez ohledu na to, co udělám,
