536
00:49:51,680 --> 00:49:53,740
Navždy si to pamatuj.

537
00:49:55,360 --> 00:49:58,970
Jang Chul Oh. Moje sestra Yeon Ji.

538
00:49:59,720 --> 00:50:01,650
