00:53:25,140 --> 00:53:26,820
Jung Hyune!

575
00:53:28,480 --> 00:53:29,770
Prosím!

576
00:53:33,190 --> 00:53:36,830
Prosím! Nechoď.

577
00:53:37,620 --> 00:53:40,020
Prosím!

578
00:53:52,210 --> 00:53:53,500
